item.description:
If you have any interest in joining a camera club we meet the first Thursday of every month.  The membership dues are $30 for an individual and $40 for a family.

At this meeting we will be selecting images to be entered into the New England Camera Club Council's photo contests.  Members of the club may enter images for consideration for the contest.  4 images will be entered in the nature category and 4 in the pictorial category.
item.how_to_find_us: We meet in the main conference room
item.name: Northern RI Camera Club Meeting
